import React, { Component } from "react";
import Banner from "../components/Banner";
import { TextField, Container } from "@material-ui/core";

class Contact extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <React.Fragment>
        <Banner title="contact us" />
        <Container>
          <form noValidate autoComplete="off">
            <TextField
              fullWidth
              id="outlined-basic"
              label="Your Name"
              variant="outlined"
              className="mb-3"
            />
            <TextField
              fullWidth
              id="outlined-basic"
              label="Your Email"
              variant="outlined"
              className="mb-3"
            />
            <TextField
              fullWidth
              id="outlined-basic"
              label="subject"
              variant="outlined"
              className="mb-3"
            />
            <TextField
              fullWidth
              id="outlined-basic"
              label="subject"
              variant="outlined"
              className="mb-3"
            />
          </form>
        </Container>
      </React.Fragment>
    );
  }
}
export default Contact;
